{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"你們是更難造的呢？還是天是更難造的呢？他曾建造了天，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"他升起它的高度，而成全它的形體，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"他使它的夜間黑暗，並顯出它的光明。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"此後，他將地面展開，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"他使地面涌出泉水來，生出植物來。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"他使山巒穩定，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"以便你們和你們的牲畜獲得享受。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"大難來臨的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"就是人將記起自己所作的善惡，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"火獄將為能見的人顯露出來的日子。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"悖逆"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"而且選擇今世生活的人，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"火獄必為他的歸宿。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"至於怕站在主的御前受審問，並戒除私慾的人，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"樂園必為他的歸宿。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"他們問你復活時在什麼時候實現，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"你怎能說明它呢？"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"惟有你的主能知它的究竟。"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"你的警告只有裨於畏懼它的人，"},{"SurahNumber":79,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"他們在見它的那日，好像在墳裡只逗留過一朝或一夕。"}]}